---
title: Chorizo and Sweet Potato Stew with kidney beans and coconut milk
description: This chorizo and sweet potato stew is a dish with plenty of flavour that takes inspiration from a myriad of different cultures and cuisines. Mild spice from garam masala is balanced beautifully by the cooling coconut milk.
